Commentary Text: Alzarri Joseph to Nitish Rana, out Caught by Shami!! Joseph brought back and he strikes straightaway! Crucial breakthrough from the tall pacer who's been in good wicket-taking form. 141kph, pitched right up around off, a risky delivery with mid-off in the ring. Rana looks to go over the man but doesn't quite get hold of it. Gives a simple catch to Shami at the edge of the circle. Maybe Rana's weight was back in the crease, expecting him to go short. Nitish Rana c Shami b Alzarri Joseph 45(29) [4s-4 6s-3]
